description:
Spinnin Records Generation Collection (2014) 

               Progressive, Bigroom, Dutch, Electro | Spinnin' Records

                 320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 05:44:42 | 800 Mb


Sunnery James and Ryan Marciano drop another banger on Spinnin'. Tribal electro big room house of the highest order. This thing just has no remorse, it will obliterate any dance floor out there! The incredible Yellow Claw proudly presents their brand new production on Spinnin'. For 'Shotgun' they take elements from dub and ragga and combine it with the fattest trap beats imaginable to create a monster release! They all play this track and the crowd goes absolutely loco when they do. 'Incredible' by Carnage & Borgore is one of those peak time productions that delivers its qualities best on a huge sound system in front of a jump happy crowd.
